cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.PL. 

The paper deals with the integration of OWL ontologies, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence and knowledge representation (cs.AI). The study of complexity of reasoning over ontologies is a topic in logic and computational complexity (cs.LO). The use of ontologies for data integration is also a topic in databases (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper deals with fragments of OWL, which is a language for representing ontologies and falls under programming languages (cs.PL).
